{"title":"动态规划入门","uid":"22080fe23e1a3d9bd1d63ab39356ea8c","slug":"动态规划专题","date":"2021-07-23T14:01:21.000Z","updated":"2021-07-24T13:29:49.507Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/动态规划专题.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/theme/动态规划.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"动态规划入门\"><a href=\"#动态规划入门\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"动态规划入门\"></a>动态规划入门</h1><h3 id=\"Day-One\"><a href=\"#Day-One\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Day-One\"></a>Day-One</h3><p><b>斐波那契数列</b></p>\n<p>通常用 <code>F(n)</code> 表示，形成的序列称为 <b>斐波那契数列</b> 。该数列由 <code>0</code> 和 <code>1</code> 开始，后面的每一项数字都是前面两项数字的和。也就是：</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>F(0) = 0，F(1) = 1<br>F(n) = F(n - 1) + F(n - 2)，其中 n &gt; 1</p></blockquote>\n<p>给你 <code>n</code> ，请计算 <code>F(n)</code> ；</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">class Solution:\n    def fib(self, n: int) -&gt; int:\n        if n &#x3D;&#x3D; 0:\n            return 0\n        elif n &#x3D;&#x3D; 1:\n            return 1\n        F &#x3D; (n + 1) * [0]\n        F[0] &#x3D; 0\n        F[1] &#x3D; 1\n        for i in range(2, n + 1):\n            F[i] &#x3D; F[i-1] + F[i-2]\n        return F[n]</code></pre>\n\n<p><b>第 N 个泰波那契数</b></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">class Solution:\n    def tribonacci(self, n: int) -&gt; int:\n        if n &#x3D;&#x3D; 0:\n            return 0\n        elif n &#x3D;&#x3D; 1 or n &#x3D;&#x3D; 2:\n            return 1\n\n        T &#x3D; (n+1) * [0]\n        T[1] &#x3D; T[2] &#x3D; 1\n        for i in range(3, n+1):\n            T[i] &#x3D; T[i-1] + T[i-2] +T[i-3]\n        return T[n]</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"Day-Two\"><a href=\"#Day-Two\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Day-Two\"></a>Day-Two</h3><p><b>爬楼梯</b></p>\n<p>假设你正在爬楼梯。需要 n 阶你才能到达楼顶。</p>\n<p>每次你可以爬 1 或 2 个台阶。你有多少种不同的方法可以爬到楼顶呢？</p>\n<p>注意：给定 n 是一个正整数。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>输入： 2<br>输出： 2<br>解释： 有两种方法可以爬到楼顶。</p>\n<ol>\n<li> 1 阶 + 1 阶</li>\n<li> 2 阶</li>\n</ol></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>输入： 3<br>输出： 3<br>解释： 有三种方法可以爬到楼顶。</p>\n<ol>\n<li> 1 阶 + 1 阶 + 1 阶</li>\n<li> 1 阶 + 2 阶</li>\n<li> 2 阶 + 1 阶</li>\n</ol></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-Python\" data-language=\"Python\"><code class=\"language-Python\"># 题目简单，每个台阶都可以由前两个台阶走过来，显然存在重叠子问题，故采用动态规划\nclass Solution:\n    def climbStairs(self, n: int) -&gt; int:\n        Stair &#x3D; (n + 1) * [0]\n        Stair[0] &#x3D; Stair[1] &#x3D; 1\n        for i in range(2, n + 1):\n            Stair[i] &#x3D; Stair[i - 1] + Stair[i - 2]\n        return Stair[n]</code></pre>\n\n<p><b>使用最小花费爬楼梯</b></p>\n<p>数组的每个下标作为一个阶梯，第 i 个阶梯对应着一个非负数的体力花费值 cost[i]（下标从 0 开始）。</p>\n<p>每当你爬上一个阶梯你都要花费对应的体力值，一旦支付了相应的体力值，你就可以选择向上爬一个阶梯或者爬两个阶梯。</p>\n<p>请你找出达到楼层顶部的最低花费。在开始时，你可以选择从下标为 0 或 1 的元素作为初始阶梯。</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"># 紧接着上一题，每个阶梯可以有前两个阶梯走来，我们需要其中最小消耗值的方式，其中也是存在重叠子问题，故也采用动态规划\nclass Solution:\n    def minCostClimbingStairs(self, cost) -&gt; int:\n        cost.append(0)\n        n &#x3D; len(cost)\n        for i in range(2, n):\n            cost[i] +&#x3D; min(cost[i - 1], cost[i - 2])\n        return cost[n - 1]</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"Day-Three\"><a href=\"#Day-Three\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Day-Three\"></a>Day-Three</h3><p><b>打家劫舍</b></p>\n<p>你是一个专业的小偷，计划偷窃沿街的房屋。每间房内都藏有一定的现金，影响你偷窃的唯一制约因素就是相邻的房屋装有相互连通的防盗系统，如果两间相邻的房屋在同一晚上被小偷闯入，系统会自动报警。</p>\n<p>给定一个代表每个房屋存放金额的非负整数数组，计算你 不触动警报装置的情况下 ，一夜之内能够偷窃到的最高金额。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>示例 1：</p>\n<p>输入：[1,2,3,1]<br>输出：4<br>解释：偷窃 1 号房屋 (金额 = 1) ，然后偷窃 3 号房屋 (金额 = 3)。<br>     偷窃到的最高金额 = 1 + 3 = 4 。</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>示例 2：</p>\n<p>输入：[2,7,9,3,1]<br>输出：12<br>解释：偷窃 1 号房屋 (金额 = 2), 偷窃 3 号房屋 (金额 = 9)，接着偷窃 5 号房屋 (金额 = 1)。<br>     偷窃到的最高金额 = 2 + 9 + 1 = 12 。</p></blockquote>\n<p>提示：</p>\n<p>1 &lt;= nums.length &lt;= 100<br>0 &lt;= nums[i] &lt;= 400</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\"># 思路比较简单，由于房间是线状的，总是从第一间或者第二间开始偷，小偷到达每一间房间的最高金额等于当前房间金额与前一间房间之前所有房间里最高金额之和\nclass Solution:\n    def rob(self, nums) -&gt; int:\n        n &#x3D; len(nums)\n        if n &#x3D;&#x3D; 0:\n            return 0\n        elif n &#x3D;&#x3D; 1:\n            return nums[0]\n        Max &#x3D; max(nums[0], nums[1])\n\n        for i in range(2, n):\n            temp &#x3D; 0\n            for j in range(i - 1):\n                temp &#x3D; nums[j] if nums[j] &gt; temp else temp\n            nums[i] +&#x3D; temp\n            Max &#x3D; nums[i] if nums[i] &gt; Max else Max\n        return Max</code></pre>\n\n","text":"动态规划入门Day-One斐波那契数列 通常用 F(n) 表示，形成的序列称为 斐波那契数列 。该数列由 0 和 1 开始，后面的每一项数字都是前面两项数字的和。也就是： F(0) = 0，F(1) = 1F(n) = F(n - 1) + F(n - 2)，其中 n &gt; ...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.9k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"动态规划","slug":"动态规划","count":1,"path":"api/categories/动态规划.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Leecode","slug":"Leecode","count":6,"path":"api/tags/Leecode.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E8%A7%84%E5%88%92%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">动态规划入门</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Day-One\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Day-One</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Day-Two\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Day-Two</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Day-Three\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Day-Three</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Dominique Yiu","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/dominique-yiu/csdn/raw/master/theme/icon.png","link":"/","description":"There is only one heroism in the world, to see the world as it is and to love it. <br /> @ <b>realrealyiu@gmail.com</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Dominique-Yiu","twitter":"https://twitter.com/KingSwi39106371","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/whatever-36-86","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_49005782","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"机器学习之岭回归","uid":"e7b94477fd527221fa10aef655891e9a","slug":"岭回归","date":"2021-05-15T16:10:35.000Z","updated":"2021-07-17T12:21:57.176Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/岭回归.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/theme/岭回归.jpeg","text":"机器学习之岭回归在线性回归模型中，有一个致命的问题，就是对于估计参数 \\omega = (X^TX)^{-1}X^TY ，如果 (X^TX) 它不可逆那么就会导致无法求出这个参数，另外如果 |X^TX| 月接近与0，会使得回归系数趋近于无穷大，这样也是无意义的。为了解决这类问题，...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.7k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"AI","slug":"AI","count":1,"path":"api/tags/AI.json"}],"author":{"name":"Dominique Yiu","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://gitee.com/dominique-yiu/csdn/raw/master/theme/icon.png","link":"/","description":"There is only one heroism in the world, to see the world as it is and to love it. <br /> @ <b>realrealyiu@gmail.com</b>","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Dominique-Yiu","twitter":"https://twitter.com/KingSwi39106371","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/whatever-36-86","csdn":"https://blog.csdn.net/qq_49005782","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"feature":true},"next_post":{"title":"Leecode：寻找两个正序数组的中位数","uid":"e28975790eb97ff1ceaf51d08f04d8d6","slug":"Leecode：Q4","date":"2021-07-20T00:17:08.000Z","updated":"2021-07-20T